name: Sanctuary: A Witch's Tale
overview: Set in a contemporary world where witchcraft is real, the story takes place in the idyllic English town of Sanctuary, where for hundreds of years witches have lived peacefully, as valued members of society. Until now…

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: When a teen sports star dies at a party, a police investigation suggests there’s more to his death than meets the eye.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Sarah seeks to disprove accusations of witchcraft against her daughter Harper whilst Abigail resorts to blackmail.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Harper makes a shocking revelation to Sarah. An accusation from Harper sends Abigail into revenge mode.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Harper’s accusations put suspicion onto her and Sarah, and a memorial vigil incites ill feeling.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Following the dunking, Sarah decides to cast a spell over the whole of Sanctuary. A revelation pushes Abi into action.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Abigail seeks to clear Dan’s name by whipping up anti-witch feeling amidst a mystery virus and evidence of dark magic.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: With Sanctuary cut off from the outside world, Abigail has free rein to exact the ultimate revenge on Sarah and Harper.
